<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.10">
<l>tirainīrc cantiramaṇ ṭalampōṟ ceṅkaṇmāṟ kēcavaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>tirunīr mukattuttu laṅkucuṭṭi tikaḻnteṅkum puṭaipeyarap</l>
<l>perunīrt tiraiyeḻukaṅ kaiyilum periyatōr tīrttapalan</l>
<l>tarunīrc ciṟuccaṇṇan tuḷḷañcōrat taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While the glittering forehead ornament,</l>
<l>shining on the sacred-water [like] face of Keśava, red-eyed Māl,</l>
<l rend="indent">like the disc of the moon on the rolling ocean,</l>
<l>moves on every side,</l>
<l>while the water that produces the fruit of the sacred water</l>
<l rend="indent">that is greater than even the Ganges rising with waves of great water</l>
<l>trickles down in little drops from [his] small penis,</l>
<l>will [he] come with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
